ch.powerunit

Annotation Type TestDelegator


  • @Documented
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=TYPE)
public @interface TestDelegator
    This annotation is used on test framework class.

    This annotation is used on test classes that are test framework. This annotation modify the validation of the method annotated with Parameters to indicate that this method receive one parameter.

    Since:
    0.2.0
    Author:
    borettim
